$ hangdiag.sql

This script dumps data required to diagnose hangs:
  • → development/databases/Oracle/Active-Session-History[ASH] dump
  • Systemstate dump with short callstacks
  • Hang analysis results (`x$ksdhng_chains`)

sa:
  → development/databases/Oracle/tools/oradebug/hanganalyze[`oradebug hanganalyze`]

  `hangdiag.sql` makes extensive use of → development/databases/Oracle/tools/oradebug/direct_access[`oradebug direct_access`]

